               feloniously and falsly making, forging, and counterfeiting, and causing and procuring to be falsly made, forged, and counterfeited, on the <rs id="t17831029-32-cd173" type="crimeDate">30th day of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831029-32-off172 t17831029-32-cd173"></join> last, a certain bill of exchange with the name 
